ygData.messageBody:
Hey everyone, I wanted to let you know about a new EQ mailing list I've created: EQ_rainbow. This mailing list is for lesbian/gay/bi/tg Everquest players.

If you're interested in subscribing, you can go to the following link:
http://www.onelist.com/subscribe/EQ_rainbow

I've included more information on the list below.

- Christina

Here is the basic blurb on the list:

A mailing list for lesbian/gay/bi/tg players of the game Everquest. Basicly a place for us to get together, chat, and have some fun!

Everquest is a great game, which specificly disallows harassment, and anti-gay organizations. You can find out more about Everquest at www.everquest.com.

This list has public content (anyone can read what you write) but private membership (no one can see who is subscribed).
